---
title: Speedy BBQ Chicken Breast Sandwiches with Dill Pickle Coleslaw
description: Super quick and full of flavour, these sandwiches pack a classic BBQ punch! Sweet and smoky sauce smothers quick-to-broil chicken. Dill pickles add zesty tang to every bite.
